---
By: Deepak Chopra
Locus:
  Page: 234
  Verse: 3
Tags:
  - Health
---
There exists in every person a place that is free from disease, that never
feels pain, that cannot age or die. When you go to this place, limitations
which all of us accept cease to exist. They are not even entertained as a
possibility. This is a place called perfect health.
